"""
PART III Income

15. Income for the purposes of the Act

(1)

Editorial note: current text valid from 2025-03-21.

For the purposes of section 15(1)(e) (income), all social security benefits are prescribed except—

(ra)

carer’s allowance supplement payable under section 81 of the Social Security (Scotland) Act 2018;
"""

benefit_is_social_security_benefit:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean

benefit_is_carers_allowance_supplement_payable_under_section_81_social_security_scotland_act_2018:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean

benefit_is_prescribed_as_income_except_carers_allowance_supplement_15_1_ra:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean
    from 2025-03-21:
        if benefit_is_carers_allowance_supplement_payable_under_section_81_social_security_scotland_act_2018: false else: benefit_is_social_security_benefit
